== 評價和回響 ==
《最後一案》的評價有好有壞。英國《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的 Sean O'Grady對該集表示讚許、在五顆星的滿分中給了四顆。他表示班尼迪克·康柏拜區和馬丁·費里曼這組搭檔仍舊演出了完美的二重奏，但也建議作品有一些需要再構想的地方<ref>{{cite web |author=Sean O'Grady |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/last-nights-tv-sherlock-the-final-problem-bbc1-a7526171.html |title=Sherlock season 4 episode 3 review: 'The Final Problem' maybe needs reimagining |publisher=The Independent |date=2016-11-04 |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2020-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725230134/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/last-nights-tv-sherlock-the-final-problem-bbc1-a7526171.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》的Michael Hogan給了五顆星，他稱讚「有笑有淚的劇情令人目不暇給……這部作品為我們創造了一對更聰明的福爾摩斯與華生」。他還推測該集可能並非劇集的完結篇，因為「它有個明顯令人意猶未盡的結尾」。<ref>{{cite web |author=Michael Hogan |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/tv/0/sherlock-episode-3-final-problem-review-exhilarating-thrill/ |title=Sherlock episode 3: The Final Problem, review: 'an exhilarating thrill-ride' |publisher=Telegraph.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2019-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107170548/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/tv/0/sherlock-episode-3-final-problem-review-exhilarating-thrill/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

然而、《最後一案》也得到了很多負面的評論。評論網站《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》的Kaite Welsh給了 B- 的評分，她表示「史蒂芬·莫法特和馬克·加蒂斯讓福爾摩斯與華生這對一代傳奇結束在哀歌般的第13集，這一集的結尾太過混亂，實在是個恥辱」<ref>{{cite web |author=Kaite Welsh |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2017/01/sherlock-review-the-final-problem-season-4-episode-4-spoilers-finale-1201769310/ |title=Sherlock Review: ‘The Final Problem’ Is A Problematic Season Finale |publisher=IndieWire |date= |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126075006/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/01/sherlock-review-the-final-problem-season-4-episode-4-spoilers-finale-1201769310/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《{{link-en|Vox媒體|Vox Media}}》的 Aja Romano評論這一集「簡直崩潰得一團混亂，邏輯成份寥寥無幾。」Romano認為這集虎頭蛇尾，並批評「簡直就像是另一套故事」<ref>{{cite web |last=Johnson |first=Nathanael |url=http://www.vox.com/2017/1/16/14279588/sherlock-finale-final-problem-review |title=Sherlock season 4, episode 3: "The Final Problem" might be the series finale. If it is, it's a huge disappointment. |publisher=Vox |date= |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111182735/https://www.vox.com/2017/1/16/14279588/sherlock-finale-final-problem-review |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。《[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]》的Christopher Stevens暨之前給了《[[六座柴契爾夫人像|六座柴契爾夫人像]]》一顆星的評價後，再給了這集零顆星的低分<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4080726/amp/CHRISTOPHER-STEVENS-Sherlock-s-clever-clever-s-stupid.html?client=ms-android-motorola|title=CHRISTOPHER STEVENS: Sherlock's now so clever-clever, it's stupid|last=Driver|first=Ben|date=|website=The Daily Mail|publisher=|access-date=2017-01-16|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118134237/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4080726/amp/CHRISTOPHER-STEVENS-Sherlock-s-clever-clever-s-stupid.html?client=ms-android-motorola|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他強烈地批判這一集的劇本、認為它糟糕透頂。表示這一集的「案」如同羽毛未全的雛鳥、不自然而且只有大學生水準，還有自我滿足的傾向。<ref>{{cite web |last=Stevens |first=Christopher |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4122872/After-enduring-shocking-self-indulgent-hyped-Sherlock-finale-exasperated-TV-critic-asks-BBC-bigwigs-fig-viewers.html |title=Do BBC bigwigs give a fig about Sherlock viewers? | Daily Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2016-10-19 |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000602/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4122872/After-enduring-shocking-self-indulgent-hyped-Sherlock-finale-exasperated-TV-critic-asks-BBC-bigwigs-fig-viewers.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

